Phrase: The person who grabbed Finchley by the collar with one hand is Blackfriar, an officer of the Out-Siders.

As the commander of the training unit and in charge of leadership, she gave no mercy for Finchley, who used to be her direct subordinate. She lifts Finchley's body and held her in mid-air while she spoke horrifying things with a benevolent expression on her face.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: By the way, Finchley? What was that gutless remark you just made?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Also how could you be so easily taken from behind? You're so out of shape, you know? Did you really just want to sit there for so long until I grab you?

Name: Finchley
Phrase: No, that's not why I...

Name: Putra
Phrase: 'Woah, Instructor Finchley is as meek as a kitten. I really wonder how strong Out-Siders officers are.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Heheh, not that big of a deal. Just a little bit♪

Name: Putra
Phrase: What do you mean by 'just a little bit'!? I've never heard of any Train Knight that could make Instructor Finchley dangle mid-air!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: It's not that I'm strong, it's that Finchley is weak.

Name: Putra
Phrase: No, no, no, of course not. If Finchley is weak, then what are we, then?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Mm. Yoshino doesn't get it either.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Oh, yes~ Yoshino. Tell her, tell her.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Chotto chotto chotto.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Oh, what's the matter? Islington's cute little fox.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: 'Lovely ma'am of St. Iris. Please don't say that Finchley Kyoukan is weak.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Finchley Kyoukan is very strong. And she's very good at teaching us how to study and how to fight. Sometimes she's a bit of a Spankin though.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Oh, really? Spankings are terrible. If she ever slaps your bum again, you can slap her back. I'm sure she's been used to that sort of thing for a long time.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Oooh- so Kyoukan likes to be smacked.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Good for you, Finchley. Your students seem to respect you.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: But unfortunately you're not up to my standards♪

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Hey, Finchley. I always told you, didn't I? I don't tolerate weak shit like what you said just now on the battlefield.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Never be an officer? Does that mean you don't intend to win or challenge me?

Name: Finchley
Phrase: 'No! Not at all! I'm trying to make it clear to my pupils that the officers of the Out-Siders are stronger...

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: To make it easier for your students to understand...

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: I see, so that's what that was all about. I'm sorry, I must have been jumping to conclusions.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: No, it's fine...

Name: Finchley
Phrase: (Oh, thank the Gods...)

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Ah, your face was just thinking 'Oh, thank the Gods'♪

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Hyahh!?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Didn't you?

Name: Finchley
Phrase: YES! I DID! I AM SO SORRY SIR!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Finchley, you're getting better at deception. I wonder if the increased desk work has made you more attuned to the moods of your superiors.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: It's no good making excuses or telling lies. You simply feared my strength. You look at my strength and think 'I can't do it', not by an officer's standards.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: You think you're no match comparing to me, Blackfriar. You think you're not competent and experienced enough. That's why you can never be an Out-Siders officer. That's what you really thought, wasn't it?

Name: Finchley
Phrase: (...It's over)

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: My lecture isn't over.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: ...Yes, you are correct, Blackfriar Sir. I am not up to your level, Blackfriar Sir.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: That's not your decision to make, is it?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: That's, you know, for me to decide.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Ggwahh!

Name: Putra
Phrase: Put her down, put her down! Finchley's head is going to snap!

Name: Finchley
Phrase: 'Br-Brackfriar Shir, thast's nawt whut whe dischusshed... The pran was to thighten Fahyette'sh...

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Change of target. Because you're saying pathetic crap.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Oh no, she's a terrifying, terrifying, person, that's what she is. She's injecting fighting spirit onto Instructor Finchley. This is a long one too.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: And she's smiling all the time...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Smiling and Spankin while smiling. Out-Sider officers are very scary.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Also, it's Spartan, not Spankin.

Name: Ohana
Phrase: Blackfriar-san, please be a little gentler with her. Sure, it's true that Finchley-chan did said some pathetic things. But you have to take into account that she's in front of her pupils...

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Oh, that's very sweet of you, Ohana, naive. But you have to teach them what's wrong, don't you? You should only spoil your children in the dorms.

Name: Putra
Phrase: (She called out Ohana!)

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: (And not only that, she said some preachy stuff!)

Name: Queensway
Phrase: (Instructor Finchley is a child!?)

Name: Queensway
Phrase: (Wait, Instructor Finchley is a, child!?)

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: I'm also known as the instructor of the Out-Siders too. I can understand why Finchley would want to show them how to be a good instructor.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: But if you want to keep your mens rea as an instructor, you have to be show them that you're strict, not just on other people, but on yourself too.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Isn't that right, Finchley?

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Y-yes. You're right. I'll be careful next time.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: How exactly?

Name: Finchley
Phrase: I-I will not be intimidated in the face of any adversary, lead my men to think of ways to win, and never make feeble statements that might make my subordinates anxious!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Smooth, but not the answer I'm looking for. You're missing the point of my previous statement.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: I WILL ALWAYS REMEMBER TO CHALLENGE MYSELF AND ALWAYS STRIVE TO BE BETTER!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Yes, well said. Be careful next time...

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Pant... Pant...

Name: Finchley
Phrase: That's why. All of you...

Name: Finchley
Phrase: The Out-Sider officers are very strong! But you and I can reach that level if we work hard! As Train Knights, you must always push your limits!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Well, I think that's enough of this farce.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: And don't worry so much about Finchley. It's a loving shout-out from her superior.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Eh, is that so?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Finchley? I'm speaking now, am I not?

Name: Finchley
Phrase: PLEASE EXCUSE MY MANNERS!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Finchley was a bit nervous because she was working with me. So I put on a bit of a show to loosen her up.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Really now? I wasn't picking on her.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Well, you called out Miss Ohana casually just now. Are you and Ohana close, Miss Blackfriar?

Name: Ohana
Phrase: Yes, we are very good friends♪ Blackfriar is my classmate~

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Classmates!? So that means you and Miss Blackfriar are both the zeroth generation of the SSS?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Yes, we are. Ohana is the dormitory monitor and I'm the deputy. We used to train together when we were young.

Name: Ohana
Phrase: Oh jeez, Blackfriar, how many years ago are we talking about~~?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Oh, how many years ago was it~~? I think Finchley was still a child?

Name: Ohana
Phrase: No, that was when you were at knighthood school, wasn't it, Blackfriar?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Oh, yes, you're right. My memories of my youth can get a bit fuzzy as I get older~

Name: Ohana
Phrase: Eheheheh~~

Name: Finchley
Phrase: ...Rule of thumb. All of you. Never talk about Officer Blackfriar's age in front of her.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Well, I've lived a bit longer than everyone else, so I think I can be reasonably useful on the battlefield, you can count on that. I may not as good as Ohana, but I'm also reasonably good at fighting.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: And, nice to meet you too, Conductor Sir.
It's nice to meet you too. It is a relief to know that Blackfriar is here.

At the same time, I also expected that the place we were about to jump into was fraught with mortal danger. The presence of Out-Sider officers here meant that we would have a difficult mission ahead of us.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: You've come this far, what's the point of stating that now? You crossed the line of death long ago when you entered the Sea of Fog.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: But it's been days since we liberated the station and established a forward base. I've never had a mission of such urgency. Lady Islington said she found a clue to the Giant Tree Route Map...

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Queensway. The honour student of St. Iris Knight Academy. Promising star recognised by Kings Cross.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Eh? Promising star? Me?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Yes, you are. You're still in-training, but you've got great potential. I bet your mentor was good at it.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: To you, a promising young woman. As a fellow knight of St. Iris, I have to ask you questions.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: 'Yes. I can answer anything...

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Queensway, would you save the world in exchange for your life?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: In exchange for my life...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Yes, I can. It is for the good of the world.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Naturally. Anyone could answer a question of this magnitude. Knights, soldiers, I'm sure they'd say the same thing as you.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Now I'll modify the question I ask you. I'll put some conditions on it.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: If you sacrifice your mind and body, you might be able to save the world. Even if you can't save it completely, you might be able to buy some time to reach that goal.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: There's no guarantee that you'll even save the world. But it might be worth a try... What I meant is that, it's a 'gamble', that you may or may not really save the world.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: The price you pay for making that gamble is eternal fear. You will suffer excruciating pain and suffering, both mentally and physically.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: The people know nothing of your achievements and will not praise you for them. You will lose all memory of what you have done and forget all your precious memories.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Your loved ones, too. They will no longer see you as you are.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: ...But will you still 'gamble'?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: That's...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: ...I don't know. I am at a loss when I heard what you just said. If I'm lost here, then I don't think I'll be able to make a decision when the time comes.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Yes, honesty is good♪

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: I'm glad to hear a good answer. If you had said 'I can do it' right here, I would have leave you here.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Leave me here... Is it just me?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Yes. Just you. Because I have received reports from King's Cross that Miss Queensway's behaviour was dangerous.♪

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Oh, no, I didn't mean to be so dangerous...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: ...No. You are right. I have, on numerous occasions, put my own people in danger because of my actions. I have put my people in danger many times. It is thanks to everyone and Conductor that I have made it through to this point.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Bravery is nothing to be ashamed of. There are many things in the world that only those with courage can achieve. The brave, the heroic, the ones who are called heroes, they have extraordinary guts.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: But courage alone is not enough to win. It is not a challenge to fight a losing battle that is not even a 'gamble'.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: You're getting really strong. That's why you need to be able to think.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: To think...

Name: Finchley
Phrase: You gain confidence and nerve with every victory, but there's a difference between winning easy victories and going through the line of death over and over again. If you keep winning battles you can win, you become overconfident. If you are overconfident, you leave yourself wide open.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Always have the mindset to keep challenging yourself. You are alive today because you won yesterday's battles. To survive tomorrow, you must win today's battles.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: This is the Sea of Fog. Our goal is the Giant Tree at the centre of it. If we lose, we die. To survive, we must win. Think of a way to win, battle by battle.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Yes, Instructor. I'll keep that in mind.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: On the battlefield, follow the instructions of Officer Blackfriar. To live and to win.

Name: Ohana
Phrase: Right? And her too, Finchley-chan. She has become quite reliable, haven't she?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: She looks different, especially in front of Queensway. Is it because she's just like Finchley herself when she was younger?

Name: Ohana
Phrase: I think she doesn't want her to make the same mistakes she made. Unlike those of us of the Zeroth Generation, she has the responsibilities of a regular unit.

Name: Ohana
Phrase: She still cared about what happened in that field training.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Wounds created by people who were killed don't heal that easily. In her case, she ruined a battle that could have been won.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: That time, Finchley interfered you, Ohana. Her actions almost wiped out our unit.

Name: Ohana
Phrase: But you were in the rear, preparing us to retreat. Thanks to Blackfriar, we were spared that. Finchley-chan and I both made it back alive.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Stop saying that. Just remembering how gutless I was makes me want to puke.

Name: Ohana
Phrase: If I was going to jump out on my own, I should have told my mates, 'Don't come'. I had to at least anticipate that my juniors would join in. If I had been as smart as Blackfriar, I could have prevented this from happening.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: That's not what I expected from you Ohana, I thought you were going to exclaim 'If only I was strong enough to fight while protecting Finchley'.

Name: Ohana
Phrase: Whaa, you make it sound like I'm the brains of the team~

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Well, Ohana has always been the brains, aren't ya~?

Name: Ohana
Phrase: Heheh~

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Eheheheh~

Name: Fayette
Phrase: Blackfriar Sir! Emergency!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: 'Emergency' doesn't cover it. Describe the situation accurately and concisely.

Name: Fayette
Phrase: The Portal is about to close at any moment!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: About to close?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Not only that, it's crawling with monsters! They're heading straight for the base!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Couldn't hold on...

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Ohana, Finchley. We have to go, now.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Yes, I'm on it.

Name: Ohana
Phrase: Let's go, Finchley. We're going to prioritize speed. Follow me closely.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Yes!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Leave the monsters that's spilling out to those two. We'll hurry up and get to the Portal.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: I'll lead with Queensway. Fayette will back us up. Understood?

Name: Fayette
Phrase: Roger that.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Queensway.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Yes, Sir. Instructor Blackfriar.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Not 'Instructor'. Just call me Blackfriar, as a member of the unit, you will protect me and be protected by me. Is that clear?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Understood.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Where we are going from here, a dangerous gamble awaits those who continue to take it. There is no such thing as a safe victory.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: We will do everything in our power to die for certain victory. Honours, elites, officers, enlisted men, nobility. Leave all such titles and ranks here.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Common sense has no place near the Giant Tree. We'll find out as soon as we walk through the Portal.
